org.transitime.ipc.data

Class IpcVehicleGtfsRealtime

  • java.lang.Object
    • org.transitime.ipc.data.IpcVehicle
      • org.transitime.ipc.data.IpcVehicleGtfsRealtime
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    java.io.Serializable
    Direct Known Subclasses:
    IpcVehicleComplete

    public class IpcVehicleGtfsRealtime
extends IpcVehicle
    Extension of IpcVehicle class so that additional info can be provided for GTFS-realtime feed. Made a separate class from IpcVehicle since the expect other interfaces, such as the JSON/XML interface, to be dominant and don't want to bog down all the other IpcVehicle requests with extraneous data.
    Author:
    SkiBu Smith
